reports.title: Top-10 of searching result for: $neodash_search_name

CALL db.index.fulltext.queryNodes('ftindexConsignee',$neodash_search_name)
YIELD node, score 
RETURN

node.name AS bol_name,
node.address_last AS address_last,
score AS match_score,

reports.title: Community's Nodes averages: $neodash_selected_name
reports.query:
MATCH (n)
WHERE n.name = $neodash_selected_name
WITH n._leid_id as leid_id
MATCH (n)-[r]-(m)
WHERE n._leid_id = m._leid_id=leid_id
RETURN
labels(m) AS label, //size: 0.6
count(distinct m) AS count, //size: 0.3
avg(m._pr_wescaled) AS pr_wescaled, //size: 0.5
avg(m.delay_count_ratio) AS delay_count_ratio, //size: 0.8
avg(m.delay_days_mean) AS delay_days_mean, //size: 0.8
avg(m.delay_days_q50) AS delay_days_q50, //size: 0.8
avg(m.delay_days_q95) AS delay_days_q95 //size: 0.8
ORDER BY label

settings.description: Averages of properties calculated for all nodes (w/o out guy) inside community.

reports.title: Community's Relationships averages: $neodash_selected_name
reports.query:

settings.description: Double click on blue {bol_name} will run a connections finding.

reports.title: Shortest: $neodash_selected_name * $neodash_selected_customer
reports.query:
WITH ["N/A", "SAME AS CONSIGNEE", "SAMERICA AS CONSIGNEE"] AS list
MATCH 
(n {name: $neodash_selected_name}),
(m {name: $neodash_selected_customer}),
p = shortestPath((n)-[:SHIPS_FOR|NOTIFY_FOR *]-(m))
WHERE none(n IN nodes(p) WHERE n.name IN list)
//WHERE none(n IN nodes(p) WHERE n.name="N/A")
RETURN p

settings.description: This is the shortest path between two entities.

reports.title: All: $neodash_selected_name * $neodash_selected_customer
reports.query:
WITH ["N/A", "SAME AS CONSIGNEE", "SAMERICA AS CONSIGNEE"] AS list
MATCH 
(n {name: $neodash_selected_name}),
(m {name: $neodash_selected_customer}),
p = allShortestPaths((n)-[:SHIPS_FOR|NOTIFY_FOR *]-(m))
WHERE none(n IN nodes(p) WHERE n.name IN list)
//WHERE none(n IN nodes(p) WHERE n.name="N/A")
RETURN p
LIMIT 10
